{"tid":2250852,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"寧願睇針灸都唔睇物理治療","createTime":"2020-10-20T11:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T08:13:09.000Z","uid":123401,"like":33,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"7a87a7a1ed338d6962e108999ccef08428c017ae","tid":2250852,"uid":123401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇親物理治療都比人拖症，收費又勁貴。成日覺得d治療只係帶黎短期既舒緩，長遠根本無咩改善到<br />\n<br />\n相反中醫唔知咩原理，但只係用一支支針都針到你好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁多舊患都係針灸先斷到尾，物理治療好似只係幫手恢復到一半咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係鄧d中醫師唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11318eec82844e29ecc059216586fe9fcf84b88f","tid":2250852,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:30:56.000Z","msg":"吉針又真係得得地"},{"pid":"d541ac2776b7e576c2895d43f3cd7beed407d3c7","tid":2250852,"uid":253039,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"乜針灸就唔會拖你症咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8c00694ba1f01aebf498d7dc5af84ed9ebcd7c","tid":2250852,"uid":335115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:21:14.000Z","msg":"你咁叻知道比人拖症？"},{"pid":"6d3b7c63f6e201db1c063cd4e6da74fed837edfc","tid":2250852,"uid":25028,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8c00694ba1f01aebf498d7dc5af84ed9ebcd7c","tid":2250852,"uid":335115,"like":2,"dislike":